window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A witch with a side hustle</b></p> <p>Star needs another paying gig while she finishes her witch training. Why not at a funeral home? It fits her goth image, and the funeral director is sort of hot...even if he does wear a suit and tie.</p> <p>Less than a day on the job as makeup artist to the dead, and Star discovers one of their accidental death clients didn’t die accidentally.</p> <p>Before she knows it, she’s neck-deep in paranormal intrigue and her completely human, way-too-nice-for-his-own-good boss is right there with her.</p>"; 
